Black Widow is officially out and many fans have been waiting with bated breathe to see what the 24th film in the Marvel Cinematic Universe had in store. After watching her other founding Avengers get their own solo films, Natasha Romanoff grabs the reins in this action-packed film about family, espionage, and creating your own path. Join us as we gush over what could possibly be the last time we ever see Nat again in this return to form for the Major Issues Podcast

